<section class='problem' id='problema'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='problem-intro fade-in'>
      <h2 class='section-title'>
        Hay dolores que <span class='text-gold'>no sanan solos</span>
      </h2>
      <div class='divider-center'>✦</div>
    </div>

    <div class='problem-content'>
      <div class='problem-text-column fade-in-left'>
        <p class='text-lead'>
          Hay duelos que no se superan con el simple paso del tiempo. Hay
          pérdidas que no se acomodan solas. Y hay dolores que, si no se honran
          y acompañan desde el amor, <em>se quedan a vivir en el alma.</em>
        </p>
        <p class='text-body'>
          Con el tiempo, este dolor silencioso se transforma en miedos, en
          barreras invisibles que te impiden vincularte con otros de manera
          segura y despiertan tu herida de abandono, una y otra vez.
        </p>
        <div class='gold-quote-box'>
          Este programa de 8 semanas no es para "olvidar". Es para <strong
            >transformar</strong
          > el dolor en sabiduría, para <strong>entender</strong> tu proceso y para
          que el duelo <strong>no dirija tu destino</strong>.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='problem-image-column fade-in-right'>
        <!-- Abstract spiritual shape representing the soul/pain -->
        <div class='soul-shape'>
          <svg viewBox='0 0 200 200' class='soul-svg'>
            <path
              d='M100 20 C 140 20, 180 60, 180 100 C 180 140, 140 180, 100 180 C 60 180, 20 140, 20 100 C 20 60, 60 20, 100 20 Z'
              fill='none'
              stroke='#d4af37'
              stroke-width='0.5'></path>
            <path
              d='M100 30 C 130 30, 170 70, 170 100 C 170 130, 130 170, 100 170 C 70 170, 30 130, 30 100 C 30 70, 70 30, 100 30 Z'
              fill='none'
              stroke='#d4af37'
              stroke-width='0.3'
              stroke-dasharray='2 4'></path>
            <circle cx='100' cy='100' r='20' fill='rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1)'
            ></circle>
          </svg>
          <div class='soul-message'>
            "Aquí no tienes que ser fuerte. <br /> Aquí solo tienes que ser tú."
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class='for-you' id='para-ti'>
  <div class='bg-overlay'></div>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='for-you-header fade-in'>
      <span class='section-subtitle'>Identificación</span>
      <h2 class='section-title'>Este camino es para ti si…</h2>
      <div class='divider-center'>✦</div>
    </div>

    <div class='cards-container'>
      <div class='luxury-card fade-in' style='--delay: 0.1s'>
        <div class='card-border'></div>
        <div class='card-content'>
          <span class='card-number'>I</span>
          <p>
            Sientes que desde la pérdida, <br /><strong
              >ya no eres la misma persona.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='luxury-card fade-in' style='--delay: 0.2s'>
        <div class='card-border'></div>
        <div class='card-content'>
          <span class='card-number'>II</span>
          <p>
            Te exiges estar bien frente a otros, <br /><strong
              >pero por dentro te sientes roto/a.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='luxury-card fade-in' style='--delay: 0.3s'>
        <div class='card-border'></div>
        <div class='card-content'>
          <span class='card-number'>III</span>
          <p>
            La culpa te visita frecuentemente <br /><strong
              >por lo que hiciste o dejaste de hacer.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='luxury-card fade-in' style='--delay: 0.4s'>
        <div class='card-border'></div>
        <div class='card-content'>
          <span class='card-number'>IV</span>
          <p>
            Has intentado seguir adelante, <br /><strong
              >pero el vacío persiste.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Problem Section */
  .problem {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    background: var(--white-pure);
  }

  .divider-center {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 1rem 0 3rem;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .divider-center::before,
  .divider-center::after {
    content: "";
    height: 1px;
    width: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold));
  }

  .divider-center::after {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
  }

  .problem-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .problem-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .text-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-lead em {
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .text-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .gold-quote-box {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-light);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffefc 0%, #fffdf8 100%);
    position: relative;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .gold-quote-box::before {
    content: "“";
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: 20px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    background: var(--white-pure);
    padding: 0 10px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .gold-quote-box strong {
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Soul Shape */
  .soul-shape {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .soul-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    animation: breathe 8s infinite ease-in-out;
  }

  .soul-message {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    width: 70%;
  }

  @keyframes breathe {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  }

  /* For You Section */
  .for-you {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    background-color: var(--white-cream);
    position: relative;
  }

  .bg-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(
      circle at 80% 20%,
      rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%,
      transparent 40%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .for-you-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .cards-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .luxury-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--white-pure);
    transition: all 0.5s var(--transition-smooth);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: default;
    /* Aspect ratio for elegance */
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .card-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-light);
    opacity: 0.5;
    transition: all 0.5s;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .card-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .card-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.5s;
  }

  .luxury-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--gray-text);
  }

  .luxury-card strong {
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .luxury-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
  }

  .luxury-card:hover .card-border {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    inset: 15px;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .luxury-card:hover .card-number {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .problem-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .gold-quote-box::before {
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .cards-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .luxury-card {
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
